  <p>To integrate Wazuh with VirusTotal, enable FIM to monitor key directories, add the integration with your VirusTotal API key in <code>ossec.conf</code>, and Wazuh will automatically send the hash of every new or modified file to VirusTotal's 70+ antivirus engines.</p>

  <h2>How does the Wazuh FIM and VirusTotal integration work?</h2>

  <p>
    <strong>FIM (File Integrity Monitoring)</strong> detects new or modified files, but it doesn't know whether they are malicious. <strong>VirusTotal</strong> analyzes hashes against more than 70 antivirus engines. By integrating them, Wazuh automatically sends each suspicious file to VirusTotal and you get alerts directly in the dashboard.
  </p>

